Term-Prompt version 0.01
========================

Term::Prompt - Print a menu to the screen and ask for an answer.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Test::Expect (to test)

